# Table / Listing

## Container
- `overflow-x-auto border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[12px]`
- Inner min-width wrapper: `min-w-[700px]` or `min-w-[800px]`
- Layout: CSS Grid with `grid-cols-[...]`

## Header Row
- Border: `border-b border-[#e0e0e0]`
- Text: `text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.6px] font-semibold text-[#7e7e7e] leading-[16px]`
- Whitespace: `whitespace-nowrap` for multi-word headers

## Data Rows
- Cells: `text-[14px] text-[#101010] leading-[24px]`
- Whitespace: `whitespace-nowrap`
- Font weight: regular; `font-semibold` for amounts
- Hover: `hover:bg-[#f5f9fe] transition-colors`
- Cursor: `cursor-pointer` for clickable rows
- Alignment: `items-center`
- Last row: NO bottom border (container border suffices)

## Column Spacing
- Gap: `gap-8` (32px)
- Time column: ~90px fixed
- Text columns: 110–140px fixed
- Flexible columns: `1fr`
- Amount: fixed width, right-aligned
- Icon column: ~40px

## Variant: Without Vertical Separators
Padding on the grid ROW, no cell borders.
```tsx
<div className="grid grid-cols-[...] border-b border-[#e0e0e0] px-6 py-3">
  <span>Header A</span>
  <span>Header B</span>
</div>
<div className="grid grid-cols-[...] px-6 py-4 hover:bg-[#f5f9fe]">
  <div>Cell A</div>
  <div>Cell B</div>
</div>
```

## Variant: With Vertical Separators
Padding on individual CELLS, `border-r` on each cell except last.
```tsx
<div className="grid grid-cols-[...] border-b border-[#e0e0e0]">
  <p className="px-6 py-3 border-r border-[#e0e0e0]">Header A</p>
  <p className="px-6 py-3 border-r border-[#e0e0e0]">Header B</p>
  <p className="px-6 py-3">Header C</p>
</div>
<div className="grid grid-cols-[...] hover:bg-[#f5f9fe] border-b border-[#e0e0e0]">
  <div className="px-6 py-4 border-r border-[#e0e0e0]">Cell A</div>
  <div className="px-6 py-4 border-r border-[#e0e0e0]">Cell B</div>
  <div className="px-6 py-4">Cell C</div>
</div>
```

## Table Icons
- Status icon (left): `size-5`, `shrink-0`
- Copy button: `size-4 text-[#00b8f5] hover:text-[#004299]`
- Chevron (right): `ChevronRight size-5 text-[#7e7e7e]`

## Rules
- DO use CSS Grid — not flexbox or `<table>`
- DO keep last row without `border-b`
- DO NOT use short inline `<div>` dividers — use cell `border-r`
- DO NOT put `px-6` on grid rows when using vertical separators
